title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected class
description: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? The output is "MySomeClass".
OB: When invoking the onStartup method of ServletContainerInitializer with a Set of Class objects, the resulting classSet does not match the expected class.
EB: The classSet should match the expected class.
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Invoke the onStartup method of ServletContainerInitializer with a Set of Class objects. 2. Verify that the resulting classSet matches the expected class.
